given revenue and number-based targets.The ideal candidate is highly self-motivated, professional, and capable of managing their workload and prioritizing tasks in a fast-paced corporate environment. </p> <ul class=role> <li>Clients Meeting ( Face to Face )</li> <li>Generate revenue</li> <li>Sell products by establishing contacts</li> <li>Getting to understand Customers requirements</li> <li>Contributes to team effort by accomplishing related results as needed</li> <li>Fieldwork(Two Wheeler is a must)</li> </ul> <p class=details><span>Skills Required:</span></p> <ol class=skills> <li>Presentation Skills</li> <li>Good communication Skills</li> <li>Client Relationships</li> <li>Negotiation</li> <li>Meeting Sales Goals</li> <li>Creativity</li> <li>Word, Excel</li> </ol> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class=panel-heading role=tab id=headingTwo> <div class=position> <p class=job-title>Business Development Executive(Inside Sales)</p> <p class=details><span>Experience:</span> 1 - 6 yrs</p> <p class=details><span>Location:</span> Gurgaon</p> <p class=details><span>Language:</span> Hindi & English / Punjabi & English</p> </div> <a class="collapsed view" role=button data-toggle=collapse data-parent=#accordion1 href="index.html#collapseTwo" aria-expanded=false aria-controls=collapseTwo><span class=view-details>View</span> <span class=hide-details>Hide</span> Details</a> </div> <div id=collapseTwo class="panel-collapse collapse" role=tabpanel aria-labelledby=headingTwo> <div class=panel-body> <div class="col-sm-12 col-xs-12 position"> <p class=details><span>Role & Responsibilities:</span> We are looking to hire an experienced, customer-oriented Business Development Executive to utilize inbound and outbound telephone calls to achieve sales targets. The BDE’s responsibilities include cross-selling or up-selling our products, receiving incoming telephone calls and assisting with customer inquiries, as well as maintaining an accurate record of all calls made and received. You should also be able to liaise with the appropriate departments to resolve customer complaints. </p> <p class=details>To be successful as a Business Development Executive, you should be persuasive and able to work in a high-pressure environment. Ultimately, a top-performing telesales executive should be able to follow sales scripts as well as demonstrate exceptional communication, negotiation, and customer service skills.</p> <ul class=role> <li>Calling existing and potential customers to persuade them to purchase company products and services.</li> <li>Recording customers’ order details accurately.</li> <li>Processing all customer orders accordingly.</li> <li>Generating leads.</li> <li>Managing customer accounts by ensuring that existing customers remain satisfied with company products and services.</li> <li>Developing and sustaining solid relationships with customers to encourage repeat business.</li> <li>Using sales scripts offered by the company to drive sales and respond to customer rejections.</li> <li>Developing in-depth knowledge of customer products and services to make suitable recommendations based on customers' needs and preferences.</li> <li>Continually meeting or exceeding daily and monthly targets with respect to call volume and sales.</li> </ul> <p class=details><span>Skills Required:</span></p> <ol class=skills> <li>Good communication Skills</li> <li>Client Relationships</li> <li>Negotiation Skills</li> <li>Meeting Sales Goals</li> <li>Creativity</li> <li>Word, Excel</li> </ol> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <p class=sub-heading>Product Marketing & Design</p> <div class=panel-group id=accordion2 role=tablist aria-multiselectable=true> <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class=panel-heading role=tab id=headingThree> <div class=position> <p class=job-title>Jr. Digital Marketer</p> <p class=details><span>Experience:</span> 2-4yrs</p> <p class=details><span>Location:</span> Bangalore</p> </div> <a role=button class=v